channel.title: [317] How Can i Remove a Ladder?
channel.description: hey guys, theres a ladder on my server how can i delete it? what CFG / FILE?

item.title: [317] How Can i Remove a Ladder?
item.dc:creator: @DevinCooley DevinCooley
item.description:
@DevinCooley wrote:

Some the file in your source in which you can spawn custom objects. Like a tree or something like that. Then use ::noclip and ::dataon or ::mypos and find the coords of the ladder object id. Then go into the files where you can spawn objects and code…

then replace the 3095, 3498 with coords for the ladder you are trying to delete.

Hope this helped!

item.title: [317] How Can i Remove a Ladder?
item.dc:creator: @ratio ratio
item.description:
@ratio wrote:

easy steps;

  1. once in-game type ::dataon
  2. locate the ladders coords.
  3. go to ObjectManager.java
  4. search the coords (of where the object is).
  5. remove it.

this is what i do anyway.
